  "text": "Beamforming is the name given to microphone array processing which acquires a high quality signal by forming a directive pattern sensitive to the propagating direction. This section explains the principle of delay-and-sum beamforming [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] and adaptive beamforming [CITATION_3] . Furthermore, acoustic source localization using delay-and-sum beamforming is described.",
